net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.validation

Class LongRangeValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.validation.AbstractValidator<V>
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.validation.StringValueValidator<LongRangeValidator>
        • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.validation.LongRangeValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Validator

    public final class LongRangeValidator
extends StringValueValidator<LongRangeValidator>
    Validates an text input that it is a valid long and in a range of values. The validation message may include parameters for the minimum and maximum of the range, {0} for the minimum and {1} for the maximum. The value range is inclusive.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
